<header class="wrap phead">
  <div class="kicker">Contact</div>
  <h1 class="display">Let's map your <span class="gold">HQ</span>.</h1>
  <p class="sub">Tell us what you're trying to see every day and where your data lives. We'll reply with whether it's a clean build or needs a closer look — and book the $250 scoping call.</p>
</header>

<section><div class="wrap">
  <div class="contact-grid">
    <form class="cform" onsubmit="alert('Demo form — wire this to Formspree, your inbox, or a backend.');return false;">
      <div class="field"><label>Name</label><input type="text" placeholder="Your name" required></div>
      <div class="field"><label>Email</label><input type="email" placeholder="you@email.com" required></div>
      <div class="field"><label>What do you trade / manage?</label><input type="text" placeholder="e.g. options day trading, small RIA, family office"></div>
      <div class="field"><label>Package you're eyeing</label>
        <select>
          <option>Not sure yet — help me choose</option>
          <option>Entry — $2,500 + $250/mo</option>
          <option>Pro — $6,500 + $650/mo</option>
          <option>All-Star — $12,000 + $1,200/mo</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field"><label>Where does your data live?</label><textarea placeholder="Broker, market data, spreadsheets, anything you'd want on the dashboard…"></textarea></div>
      <button class="btn btn-gold" type="submit" style="width:100%">Send &amp; request scoping call</button>
      <p class="note" style="margin-top:12px">Prefer to book directly? Use the calendar link →</p>
    </form>

    <div class="cinfo">
      <div class="row"><div class="k">Book a call</div><div class="v"><a href="#" style="color:var(--gold)">[Your Calendly link]</a> — 20 min, $250 (credited to your build)</div></div>
      <div class="row"><div class="k">Email</div><div class="v">hello@critterlabs.io</div></div>
      <div class="row"><div class="k">Studio</div><div class="v">CritterLabs — AI &amp; Algorithmic Engineering</div></div>
      <div class="row"><div class="k">Live work</div><div class="v"><a href="https://stoptions.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">stoptions.ai</a> · <a href="https://critterlabs.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">critterlabs.io</a></div></div>
      <div class="row"><div class="k">What happens next</div><div class="v">We review your data sources, confirm feasibility, and send a short proposal with a fixed price and timeline before any build starts.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div></section>

